            "title": "A股窄幅偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段窄幅偏軟，滬股跌幅低於0.1%，深股現跌0.3%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指開報3350，跌2點0.06%，現報3350，跌1點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10190，跌7點或0.07%，現報10165，跌31點或0.32%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3848，跌4點或0.1%，現報3848，跌4點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2028，跌1點或0.05%，現報2021點，跌7點或0.35%。</p>\n</div>",
