            "title": "港股開升80點   晶片股挫華虹瀉9.68%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開報22856，升80點或0.35% ; 恒生科技指數開5225，跌3點或0.06%;  恒生國企指數開報8320點，升19點或0.24%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交24.47億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯國際(00981)首季盈利增1.62倍，預告次季收入降，開報42.5元，跌5.87%，成交居首。華虹半導體(01347)大挫9.22%，報32元。首季溢利380萬美元，按年大跌逾88%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西藏水資源(01115)升9.68%，報0.34元，成交入20大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升1.15%，報122.9元 ; 騰訊(00700)升0.4%，報500元 ; 美團(03690)升1.13%，報143元 ; 小米(01810)升0.59%，報51.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友邦(01299)升1.23%報61.9元 ; 滙控(00005)升0.87%，報87.1元。</p>\n</div>",
